| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0964 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 56c95f09-3d20-5ed5-b5aa-d08d98a6b6a4"
